    Interventions to improve adenoma detection rates for colonoscopy.

Pubmed   Journal   ReadQx 
Interventions to improve the performance of upper GI endoscopy quality indicators.
To date, data on interventions aimed to improve these indicators are scarce. We systematically reviewed the literature to identify interventions and measures demonstrated to improve the performance of previously established upper endoscopy quality indicators. We also identified evidence gaps and opportunities for improvement in this area.
